FR1 : User Registration and Login
The system shall allow users to register an account and log in using a valid username and password to access the system.

FR2 : Browse and Search Books
The system shall allow users to browse book categories and search for books by title,author or genre.

FR3 : View Book Details
The system sahll allow users to view detailed information of a selected book, including price, description, and availability.

FR4 : Add Books to Shopping Cart
The system shall allow users to add selected books to a shopping cart and update the quantity before checkout.

FR5: Checkout and Place Order
The system shall allow users to proceed to checkout,confirm their order, and receive an order confirmation after successful purchase.
